                                                                           PULL REQUEST


1> Pull request = A pull request is a request to merge changes from one branch into another
                 branch,usually into the main branch.


2> why do we use pull request?
= we use pull requests to:
 #> review code before merging.
 #> prevent bugs from reaching the main branch.
 #> keep the main branch stable.
 #>improve code quality.
 #> enable team collabration.


3> code review

= code review is the process of reviewing another developers code
 before merging into the main branch.      

purpose: improve code quality.
         finds bugs early.
         maintain coding standards.


4> merge pull request
  
 = merge pull  request combines the approved chnages from the feature branch
 into the main branch.

 Workfllow:
 
 1. create pull request.
 2. code review.
 3. approval.
 4. merge pull request.
 5. main branch is updated.
 6. team members pull the latest changes.

